Scientists found out that

154
00:07:19,573 --> 00:07:24,741
benzene can pass through our skin and harm us.

155
00:07:24,741 --> 00:07:28,224
What about something that is large and polar?

156
00:07:28,224 --> 00:07:32,909
Well, a molecule like this might be sugar, or glucose.

157
