Glucose cannot pass through the cell membrane.

158
00:07:36,700 --> 00:07:38,071
It's large and it's polar;

159
00:07:38,071 --> 00:07:40,106
it's the complete opposite to what

160
00:07:40,106 --> 00:07:42,772
the cell membrane wants to let through.

161
00:07:42,772 --> 00:07:44,503
So glucose will have to be absorbed

162
00:07:44,503 --> 00:07:47,251
by our cells through other means,

